name: WorkFlowy : Zen Colour Labels
description: Add ( up to 140 ) coloured labels for visual enhancement of your WorkFlowy lists.

user.name: Stefano-Rausch
user.about: Simplicity Is the Ultimate Sophistication — L. da Vinci

additional_info:
Version 1.0.0

Either use ( one of ) the 140 predefined HTML colour names to add ( visual ) meaning to an item or list — both tag variants # and @ are available. Alternatively, add your tags to the colour of your choice.

See the #pin tag example in the CSS source code, which links to #orange / @orange.

Shared ( view only ) list: https://workflowy.com/s/Ax6UaDplMf

Happy WorkFlowy'ing.
